
# MyFormula Privacy Policy
  Last updated: March 2026

## Introduction
   MyFormula is a calculator and converter application that allows users to create and run custom formulas for everyday calculations.
Your privacy is important. This Privacy Policy explains what information the app collects and how it is used.

## Information We Collect
   MyFormula does not collect, store, transmit, or share any personal information.
The application operates entirely on your device.
The app does not collect:
- Names
- Email addresses
- Phone numbers
- Location data
- Device identifiers
- Contacts
- Photos or files
- Usage analytics

## Local Data Storage
   MyFormula stores certain information locally on your device only so the app can function properly.
### This may include:
- Custom calculators created by the user
- Saved formulas
- App settings or preferences
### This data:
- remains only on the user's device
- is never transmitted to external servers
- is not accessible by the developer
- Users may optionally export or import calculator files manually.

## Third-Party Services
   MyFormula does not use third-party services, including:
analytics services
advertising networks
tracking tools

## Data Security
   Because MyFormula does not transmit or store data outside the user's device, all saved information remains under the control of the user.

## Children's Privacy
   MyFormula does not knowingly collect personal information from anyone, including children under the age of 13.

## Changes to This Privacy Policy
   This Privacy Policy may be updated occasionally. Updates will be reflected by changing the Last updated date at the top of this page.

